<para style="q1">

<verse number="2" style="v" />Everyone says empty words to his neighbor;</para>

<para style="q1">everyone speaks with flattering lips and a double heart.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="3" style="v" />Yahweh, cut off all flattering lips,</para>

<para style="q1">every tongue declaring great things.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="4" style="v" />These are those who have said, "With our tongues will we prevail.</para>

<para style="q1">When our lips speak, who can be master over us?"</para>
